{"id":"serug","term":"Serug","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Branch, the father of Nahor (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 11:20\">Gen. 11:20-23</a>); called Saruch in <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Luke 3:35\">Luke 3:35</a>.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 11:20","Luke 3:35"]}